headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Get the Still Slipping Friend Tee
content: No one likes being known as a bandwagon fan. Let your social circle know that you’ve been blasting Still Slipping since Joy Orbison was struggling to get a signal out beyond Mirror Park. Allcomers will receive the Still Slipping Friend Tee free of charge for playing any time this week. It’s like wearing your plus-five to the exclusive party on your chest.
